    aiDescription: "Inspired by the hard-drinking author, a casual lounge bar specializing in freshly mixed cocktails.",
    reviews: [{"authorName": "Isla Muir", "authorPhoto": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXu1i9nHUl19CVUcTykzYEGcjpLE0NFsk9GbgdcrSqP0v0-rfienw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5", "rating": 5, "text": "This is the most amazing cocktail bar, 100% worth coming for. All the cocktails are amazing - nothing is bad here. Plus the servers are super knowledgeable about the drinks and totally elevated the experience.", "relativeTime": "a month ago"}, {"authorName": "Adrian", "authorPhoto": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQUFiRIqcsvMzk2rlWpTorTAFDky4zIfFVCkubBa64abY8tA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4", "rating": 5, "text": "We wend for cocktails on Friday night at Hemingway bar and we were not disappointed, super friendly team when we arrived and were shown to our table. Were Marina introduced herself and looked after us for the time we were there, she is super knowledgeable and so friendly. We had a few cocktails each but for me it was the Mezcal cocktail that Marina recommended that was so delicious. If you come to Prague you have to have cocktails at Hemingway’s.\nYou need to book a table between 5-7pm then it’s first come first served. I’m", "relativeTime": "a month ago"}, {"authorName": "Nevena", "authorPhoto": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4Ka6Nh1q3JbLLPDfJxyuqhvDGVYxpfBMcIhpC-hGRmTWYys4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3", "rating": 5, "text": "Tonight we visited Hemingway Bar. Even though we didn’t have a reservation, we were offered seats at the bar, which turned out to be a great experience.\n\nThe bartender working right by the entrance (we were seated at the corner of the bar) was exceptionally kind, welcoming, and truly knowledgeable about his craft. We are very grateful for the wonderful service and especially for fulfilling our special request. When we asked for something unique, he made a real effort to understand our preferences and created something perfectly suited to our taste.\n\nHighly recommended, and we truly hope to visit again.\nAll the best from Vienna and Dubai. 🥰🤌\n\nP.s we had all together 4 drinks and one snaći", "relativeTime": "2 months ago"}, {"authorName": "Danail Dobrev", "authorPhoto": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtvdO5zCjjMs2ivoZZZYmk2KCtmoMxafgMX5xB1m-JP0fpG4vX=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4", "rating": 5, "text": "Hemingway Bar is definitely a must-visit spot in Prague. From the moment you step inside, the place impresses with its charm, elegant atmosphere, and cozy yet sophisticated vibe.\n\nThe staff are absolutely outstanding. Our waiter was incredibly attentive, very talkative, and constantly helping us choose cocktails based on our preferences. His recommendations were spot on, and the whole experience felt personal and relaxed rather than rushed or formal.\n\nThe cocktails themselves were exceptional, beautifully balanced, creative, and clearly made with great attention to detail. You can really feel the passion behind every drink, which makes the experience even more special.\n\nOverall, Hemingway Bar combines excellent service, high-quality cocktails, and a unique charm that makes it unforgettable. A perfect place for a classy evening drink and an experience that truly lives up to its reputation.", "relativeTime": "2 months ago"}, {"authorName": "JENNY MIU", "authorPhoto": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMTsrIZTagd_gh8Iw1AXiuIqQT5KBTHppv2Lvj4gsCnJ2L8uRV=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5", "rating": 4, "text": "Went for drinks and snacks, and the service was extremely friendly and very knowledgeable about all the drinks. The staff made great suggestions and offered plenty of good options. We had a fantastic time there as a group of eight ladies. Highly recommend!", "relativeTime": "3 months ago"}],
