    reviews: [{"authorName": "Ema Mimovic", "authorPhoto": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4Jz2m5YLSEBYOioHTsMYz7SwRk_I71JIr6x_o0T0Nz9sZyjkp=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo", "rating": 5, "text": "The best cocktail bar in Prague and one of the best ones I’ve ever encountered. The cocktails are amazing, as is the whole concept of the bar. The service is impeccable,\nprofessional but warm. But the thing that made me come back three times to this place is it’s atmposhpere - insane music, interior,\nand finally the staff and the bartenders. They are responsible for making the place feel so welcoming and addictive, such kind people. If I could give a 7 star review i would. I hope I’ll visit again soon. Thank you for making my trip memorable ", "relativeTime": "2 months ago"}, {"authorName": "Harriet French", "authorPhoto": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1ZWf4ZBb0UDpVG7VLhhH1KZmVjC_mPP_CJf79UsxbHirRrXA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo", "rating": 5, "text": "Absolutely phenomenal cocktail bar! From the moment we walked in, the atmosphere was vibrant, stylish, and welcoming. The best place to sit is definitely at the bar, where you really get to experience the energy of the place and watch the cocktails being crafted. What truly made the night unforgettable was Marco—he was absolutely amazing. Friendly, attentive, and incredibly knowledgeable, his recommendations were spot on, and you could tell he genuinely loves what he does. The cocktails were perfectly made, beautifully presented, and full of flavor. Thanks to Marco’s exceptional service and the overall top-tier experience, this place easily earns five stars. Can’t wait to return! 🍸✨", "relativeTime": "3 months ago"}, {"authorName": "Cindy de Vos", "authorPhoto": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQKGSBfRa9B9LKNxnMlfBEkksVoTtDwM6vxfhEcCv3YtAAFPs=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3", "rating": 5, "text": "What a bar! It's tucked away in the old town. I knocked on the door (unnecessary 🫣)—you often see that at bars, but not here. We had a spot at the bar, which was extra cool to watch the preparation. Sometimes with adapted lighting and music. Bartender Jeff listens and adjusts the cocktails accordingly. How special. I also love the show element, so if you're looking for delicious cocktails, an experience, and a show, you're in the right place. I tried four different cocktails.", "relativeTime": "2 months ago"}, {"authorName": "George Firican", "authorPhoto": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCCSQLYOKrfh6vUVf6P5omBRRkQpHrdkXnEFFo2wHvL5s_IXji=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5", "rating": 5, "text": "Truly unique and unbelievable! The cocktails I’ve had were some of the most different cocktails I’ve had at any other bar. The staff was fantastic and the presentation and story of each cocktail made everything memorable. Also had the pate which was simply delicious. I would recommend this for a different kind of bar experience.", "relativeTime": "5 months ago"}, {"authorName": "Dawn Tombley", "authorPhoto": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIltM-X_EQBuUdcKM6f04qnRJHl4ACGUAn3OEfW9wXpAvII2w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo", "rating": 5, "text": "Such a fun and unique place to get a cocktail!! The blue light menu was a fun touch! We were there earlier in the evening, around 9pm on a weekday, so the bar wasn’t too busy yet. Our bartender took her time and crafted a cocktail based on our preferences and taste!", "relativeTime": "7 months ago"}],
